# Nikolayevsky, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Nikolayevsky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Tarbagataysky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 1,295 as of 2010. There are 26 streets.
Geography
Nikolayevsky is located 43&nbsp;km northeast of Tarbagatay (the district's administrative centre) by road. Lesnoy is the nearest rural locality.
